 This product has not been approved the F DA approval in the USA and is Investigational use only in the USA. The performance characteristics of this product have not been established by the F D A to date. However, this product has achieved CE mark approval for European and Asian market and was made from a ISO 13485 certified facility for high level immunology testing. The technology is patent pending in various patent offices around the world.

